298
00:17:39,583 --> 00:17:42,207
<i>♪ I don't need your tiny hands ♪</i>

299
00:17:42,208 --> 00:17:44,207
<i>♪ And your never-ending failed plans ♪</i>

300
00:17:44,208 --> 00:17:48,291
<i>♪ You thought you were so devious ♪</i>

301
00:17:48,292 --> 00:17:51,582
<i>♪ But it's me, I'm the real evil genius ♪</i>

302
00:17:51,583 --> 00:17:53,207
<i>♪ One, two, three, four ♪</i>

303
00:17:54,417 --> 00:17:58,416
<i>♪ I'm gonna rise up like a hurricane ♪</i>

304
