305
00:18:02,250 --> 00:18:05,082
<i>♪ Fill the world with hurt and pain ♪</i>

306
00:18:05,083 --> 00:18:08,416
<i>- ♪ Say my name ♪
- ♪ Karen ♪</i>

307
00:18:08,417 --> 00:18:12,416
<i>♪ I am the real evil mastermind ♪</i>

308
00:18:12,417 --> 00:18:16,207
<i>♪ I rule the world
Through space and time ♪</i>

309
00:18:16,208 --> 00:18:19,291
<i>♪ Take it all and make it mine ♪</i>

310
00:18:19,292 --> 00:18:23,416
<i>- ♪ Say my name ♪
- ♪ Karen ♪</i>

311
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:28,958
